  "title": "Building Service Technician [ Night Shift |10pm - 7am | Preschool Project ]",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Maintenance Technician - Preschool Projects</strong></li><li><strong>5 day | 10pm - 7am</strong></li><li><strong>Salary: $2800 - $3500 + Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Work location: Labrador Park MRT walking distance</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Requirement: </strong></p><ul><li><p>Relevant Diploma / Higher Nitec / Nitec with 3 years of relevant experience</p></li><li><p>5 years of relevant working experience in major building maintenance or construction projects.</p></li><li><p>Possess a Class 2B / 3 licence with own transport.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Preventative maintenance and ensure all facilities operate efficiently and conform to operating standards.</p></li><li><p>Hands-on in meeting urgent repairs/complaints on electrical services, plumbing, and sanitary requests.</p></li><li><p>Proper maintenance of interior and exterior walls of buildings, appliances, and equipment in the building.</p></li><li><p>Conduct day-to-day inspection activities, checking building wear & tear and defects.</p></li><li><p>Mobilise and supervise contractors on major / rectification works.</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with all regulatory and safety regulations.</p></li><li><p>Comply with company safety guidelines and procedures.</p></li><li><p>Ensure accurate updates/reports are completed for all work progress and completion.</p></li><li><p>Monitor and control expenses within all areas of the department.</p></li><li><p>Lead and mentor a team of maintenance technicians.</p></li><li><p>Any other duties assigned, including support for new school projects.<br /></p><p><br />#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p></p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p><p></p></li></ul>",
